Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm scared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm scared to get\Nto the heart of my own mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're doing good work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But how can I say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:38.69,Clang,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BOYS' FLIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't dig deeper,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the readers won't be\Nable to see you in the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're 29, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of a tough fit\Nfor our magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}26 more days until the 2006 World Cup\Nbegins in Germany...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Every day, the words cross my mind.\N"If I had done this back then..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}But they don't take\Nthe sincere form of regret.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}The words are just an excuse\Nthat come to mind, then disappear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm scared to get\Nto the heart of my own mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.81,0:01:14.35,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ERASED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out on a delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out on a delivery, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.40,0:01:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujinuma, don't eat any pizza on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't get it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is that, a Gen Y joke?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't planning to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That girl says the same thing\Nto me every time I see her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In fact, it's the only thing she's said to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't seem like\Nshe has any special feelings for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Weird girl...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, not like I'm interested\Nin high school girls...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm positive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It happened again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What seems out of place?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, trucker! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fujinuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shouldn't have gotten involved!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you okay?!\N- That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That thing where my life\Nflashes before my eyes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There, see?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing good comes of getting\Ninvolved with strangers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My dying doesn't make any difference.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His eyes opened.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Fujinuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were out for two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who you are\Nand why you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Fujinuma, 29 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing a truck\Nand got into an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good! The doctor said\Nyou hardly suffered any injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to call someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A friend or girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. There's nobody\NI want to bother telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Snip-snip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Gen Y joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you're covered\Nwith a thin membrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem like the type\Nwho opens up to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You never laugh either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I do kind of see you in a new light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You saved a kid's life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say the truck driver died\Nof a heart attack while driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After that, the truck\Ncrashed into a warehouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so you and the driver\Nwere the only casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Casualties...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After I explained everything\Nto the manager,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he said, "Tell him not to worry about the bike\Nor the car he hit, just come back to work."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You smiled for a second there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri, why do you work there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you got\Nright to the heart of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. No one's ever\Nasked me that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you're gonna ask me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you tell other people\Nabout your dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,don't you think, like,\N"But what if it doesn't happen for me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not especially\Nembarrassed to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like if you say\Nthe words over and over,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it'll actually happen\Nsomewhere along the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those words...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For some reason, they resonate with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not going to tell you\Nwhat it is, Fujinuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we're close or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll tell the nurse you're awake,\Nthen I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Weird girl...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I call the phenomenon "Revival."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I know it's not beneficial\Nfor me, I always get involved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I usually go back\Nbetween one and five minutes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}where everything is the same as before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's always right before\Nsomething bad happens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I find myself searching for the thing\Nthat doesn't feel right,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as if someone put me there\Nwith the order to "Prevent it!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a result, I've kept trouble\Nfrom happening again and again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In most cases, negative\Nincidents just come out even.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once in a while, it turns negative for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the hospital,\Nbut you were still sleeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which was boring so I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is your head all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, they said\Nit was a head-on collision.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stay with you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My adorable son's head\Nhit a moving vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The least I can do is watch over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I only have one futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a sleeping bag in the closet.\NThat works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! I'll reimburse you\Nfor the hospital charges!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it. We'll use it\Nto pay for my room here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm her son,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but even I can't believe she's 52 years old,\Nbecause the woman never changes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, can you get to Ueno\Nwithout changing trains?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. Figures. You're here\Nfor sightseeing, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have come all the way from Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'd get bored having to\Nlook at your face every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You haven't even seen me\Nfor a full day yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I took your futon and TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather have that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,than try to be quiet if I go to the bathroom\Nin the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you don't have to tiptoe around me\Nif you use the toilet in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yokai...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}On to our next story.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}The first-grade girl from Saitama\Nwho went missing yesterday evening{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}was found safe and sound\Nthis morning on a road in Yokohama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}She was taken to the hospital\Nbut suffered no injuries.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:09:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What happened in the neighborhood\Nwhen you were in fifth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}The Ina Police Station has reported\Nthat an unemployed man{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your memories are probably hazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}from Nishi-ku, Yokohama\Nwas with the girl at the scene.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We tried desperately then
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}He has been arrested on suspicion\Nof abducting a minor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to get you kids to forget\Neven a little of what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your life was in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I was in fifth grade...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An abduction...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two of my classmates went missing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go! Go, go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:10:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I was little, a local guy,\NYuuki, often played with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His name really wasn't Yuuki,\Nbut that's what I called him{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because he'd always say,\N"Yuuki, yuuki! Courage, courage..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-Want me to guess about the most\Np-popular kid in your class?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's cheerful and good at sports.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He speaks his mind\Nand sometimes screws around,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but is serious\Nwhen it comes to one thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's incredible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Popular people are usually that guy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-What if you tried imitating him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In one or two areas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as much as you can, without being\Nembarrassed, but with courage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Six months after the disappearances,\NJun Shiratori was arrested{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as a serial kidnapper and murderer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was Yuuki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Episode 1\NFlashing Before My Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bought way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it too heavy for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can have curry for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I told you not to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back and get you another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it too heavy for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can have curry for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Revival?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I told you not to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back and get you another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap. I don't know what it is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's gonna happen?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom... Would you look around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you... have a weird feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you once told me\Nthe same thing a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was about a small fire back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was he... looking at me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing happened?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujinuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.66,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SCHOOL ROUTE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it! Your mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she was your big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe in yokai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But are you fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Airi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making curry for dinner.\NWould you like to eat over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am Airi Katagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the invite!\NI'll help you make it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's coming over?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You drew manga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. You've got\Nyour own Wikitanika entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do a search on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not great. That's why\NI don't want you to do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At first I thought you were too young\Nto be his girlfriend, but you're not his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, you're a good cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we're not dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To me, Fujinuma is, how can I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A friend I can respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is it too spicy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll give you a lift to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should spend the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri is a high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having me over\Nfor dinner, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep an eye out for cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's my co-worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at her\Nas potential wife material.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have a chance with that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She said she respects you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was just being polite.\NDon't take it seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That Airi girl isn't the diplomatic type.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, the landlady\Ncame over for the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru... About this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the supermarket parking lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The abduction case was never solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm obviously kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:06.06,Sign Right,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Hokkaido Elementary School Student Serial Killer Case
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:06.06,Sign Left,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Last Serial Killer\N of the Showa Era\N\NDeath-row Inmate Jun Shiratori
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:08.52,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NIPPON\NSHOWA'S MOST SHOCKING CRIMES
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:11.98,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KAYO HINAZUKI (10 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That girl was one of my classmates,\None who was abducted 18 years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kayo Hinazuki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was always at the park alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not like we were friends, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the last time I saw Hinazuki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I could've saved her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I'd said, "Let's walk home together,"\NHinazuki would still be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the thought\NI wanted to forget the most.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Mom probably really did\Ntry to erase it from my memory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you don't dig deeper,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:16:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the readers won't be\Nable to see you in the work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Wa" on the plate means it's a rental.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was definitely\Nan attempted abduction.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did he change his mind\Nbecause he saw me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He hid his face when our eyes met.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He knew me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I know him from someplace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's on the tip of my tongue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where? When?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Serial Abductions and Murder\NOne Culprit Responsible for Kidnappings
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That man, he...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The killer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It may not have been Shiratori after all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sachiko Fujinuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}18 years ago, so the statute\Nof limitations is up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm positive he committed the same crime\Nwith the same basic M.O. over and over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That case isn't closed yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to talk to Satoru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has finally come\Nto talk to him about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have to... call Satoru...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tell him not to come home...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I have to apologize.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I could've saved her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure it wasn't Yuuki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It wasn't Yuuki, Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should have believed him then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if the police didn't...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should've believed him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Satoru...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off! See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- See you tomorrow!\N- See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about I guess what you had\Nfor breakfast this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With as much as she made, of course\NI'm gonna eat it for breakfast too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, ask your mom\Nif I can put in a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That curry was so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't your house back in Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At least lock the door.
